==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: xiǎo niǎo yī rén

===Etymology===
Literally: (as cute and helpless as) a little bird that must rely on a human in order to survive.

===Idiom===
'''[[小]][[鳥]][[依]][[人]]'''

# The appearance of a woman or a child who is dependant upon others, and is also dainty and cute.

===Alternate forms===
[[小鸟依人]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

